languages.text: "Добрались, Золото Трона! И даже не по кусочкам. Неплохо... Только не думайте расслабляться! До конца пути еще слишком далеко".
"By the Golden Throne, we made it! And all in one piece. Not bad... But we can't relax just yet — we've still got a long way to go."

languages.text: 「黄金の玉座の導きだ、やったね！これでひとつにつながる。悪くないよ…。でも、まだ一息つけないね…ここから先が長いんだから」
languages.original_text: "By the Golden Throne, we made it! And all in one piece. Not bad... But we can't relax just yet — we've still got a long way to go."

languages.text: “黄金王座在上，我们成功了！居然还活着，真不错……但还不能掉以轻心，前面的路还很长。”
languages.original_text: "By the Golden Throne, we made it! And all in one piece. Not bad... But we can't relax just yet — we've still got a long way to go."

languages.text: « Par le Trône d'Or, nous avons réussi ! Et nous sommes en un seul morceau. Pas mal... Mais l'heure n'est pas encore au repos... Nous ne sommes pas au bout de nos peines. »
languages.original_text: "By the Golden Throne, we made it! And all in one piece. Not bad... But we can't relax just yet — we've still got a long way to go."

languages.text: «¡Por el Trono Dorado, lo hemos conseguido! Y de una sola pieza. Nada mal... Pero de momento no podemos relajarnos; aún nos queda tela que cortar».
languages.original_text: "By the Golden Throne, we made it! And all in one piece. Not bad... But we can't relax just yet — we've still got a long way to go."

languages.text: "Beim Goldenen Thron, wir haben es geschafft! Noch dazu in einem Stück! Nicht übel ... Aber noch können wir uns nicht entspannen ... vor uns liegt noch ein langer Weg."

languages.text: "Altın Taht adına, başardık! Üstelik tek parçayız. Fena değiliz ama henüz tedbiri elden bırakamayız. Daha gidecek çok yolumuz var."
